**Overview**

This dashboard is a health overview related to the RecordedFuture integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the health of the ingestion of indicators from RecordedFuture.  

It shows the ingestion rates and provides a few filters for drilling down to specific indicator types retrieved from RecordedFuture.
